HEADWORD: Rampageous
<hw>Ram*pa"geous</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧m*p⟦amac⟧"j⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Characterized by violence and passion; unruly; rampant.</def>
